Description: Hand Selected For You By Nissan Of Omaha - While anyone can design a car that stands out in a crowd, can they also make it perform like nothing else? That is exactly what Nissan did with the 2013 Juke. Shown here in Sapphire Black this SL AWD model comes with 1.6L DOHC turbocharged 4-cylinder that generates a grin-inducing 188 horsepower. Nissan's Xtronic CVT w/Sport mode allows the Juke to achieve up to 30mpg proving efficiency and performance can work together beautifully. 17-inch aluminum-alloy wheels, unique turn signals and 370Z inspired taillights complete the aggressive look of the exterior. Check out our pictures and you'll notice the expressive style continues into the cabin which has been inspired by today's sport bikes. The painted center console and door trim refuse to blend in and you'll find it hard not to notice the gauges inspired by generations of motorsports. Standard goodies consist of a Rockford Fosgate audio system, Nissan's Intelligent Key, leather-appointed seats, an advanced Navigation System w/touch screen, power moonroof and the innovative Integrated Control (I-CON) System. With performance being a Juke staple, it's no surprise it performs well when it comes to keeping you safe. Six airbags, Vehicle Dynamic Control (VDC), Traction Control System (TCS) and high-strength steel side-door guard beams are just a few of the features made standard for your protection. If weather conditions deteriorate the torque-vectoring all-wheel drive will give you confidence even in the worst of road conditions. You are a unique individual so shouldn't you drive something just as unique as you? Now you can with the rally-inspired Juke. What are you waiting for? Print this page and call us Now...
